*portage-2.1-r1 (21 Jun 2006)

  21 Jun 2006; Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org> +portage-2.1-r1.ebuild:
  2.1-r1 revbump. This fixes bugs #85576, #96331, #116637, #123677, #126793,
  #133740, #136199, #136208, #136236, #136278, #136313, #136404, #136532
  136705, #136818, #136947, #137032, #137177, and #137269.  For compatibility
  with catalyst, the change in unmerge behavior from bug #118515 has been
  reverted.

*portage-2.1.1_pre1-r1 (18 Jun 2006)

  18 Jun 2006; Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org> +portage-2.1.1_pre1-r1.ebuild:
