*portage-2.1_rc2-r3 (25 May 2006)

  25 May 2006; Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org> +portage-2.1_rc2-r3.ebuild,
  +files/bug_101196_wget_timeout.patch:
  Revbump for bugs #84150, #101196, #131779, and #133804.  The ELIBC and
  USERLAND expansions have been added to IUSE.  In >=portage-2.1_rc2-r1 they
  are hidden from emerge output by USE_EXPAND_HIDDEN (see make.conf.5).

  25 May 2006; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  portage-2.0.54-r2.ebuild, portage-2.1_rc2-r2.ebuild:
  Portage now depends on >=app-shells/bash-3.0. Fixes bug #133218.

